{"tid":2401860,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"Fuze Tea檸茶有冇替代品","createTime":"2021-02-10T05:03:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-10T09:16:48.000Z","uid":384047,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"77294a06a9a6d872dfdc3309a6dce134b27aed11","tid":2401860,"uid":384047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T05:03:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UEDp2YE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUEDp2YE.jpg&h=4879844d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n半糖甜度啱啱好，檸檬味又清新<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 差唔多日日飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但已經停咗產成年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其他檸茶又冇檸味又糖水咁真係比狗飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n萬能嘅連登巴打有冇低甜平民檸茶可以推薦下 等我食晏都有包野飲下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ece65e21f1b783f7e6fcae299a1f1115b6e45d33","tid":2401860,"uid":17641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T05:05:52.000Z","msg":"759日版lipton<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7579d14f3eb8dadfb0b7a356852c887e5091481e","tid":2401860,"uid":384047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ece65e21f1b783f7e6fcae299a1f1115b6e45d33","tid":2401860,"uid":17641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T05:05:52.000Z","msg":"759日版lipton<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T05